To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Hikkake _hikkake;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_hikkake = Hikkake(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_hikkake.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "hikkake", _hikkake.Current.Value);
}

symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
